com.martinambrus.adminAnything.events

Class AARemoveIgnoredCommandEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bukkit.event.Event
      • com.martinambrus.adminAnything.events.AARemoveIgnoredCommandEvent

  • public class AARemoveIgnoredCommandEvent
extends org.bukkit.event.Event
    Event which is fired up when we need to remove a command from the list of ignored commands via /aa_unignorecommand. As a security measure, this event will only be accepted by AdminAnything if it originates from the correct AdminAnything command class.
